      <title>对冲基金创始人 Sanjay Shah 卷入 14 亿英镑税务骗局审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-on-trial-in-uk-over-1-4-billion-tax-scam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金创始人桑杰·沙阿 (Sanjay Shah) 被指控为“精心策划”的 Cum-Ex 交易计划的幕后策划者，该计划在伦敦民事审判开始时诈骗了丹麦政府 14 亿英镑（合 17 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-on-trial-in-uk-over-1-4-billion-tax-scam</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗紧张局势缓和，石油稳定，国债下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周股市开盘表现积极，而债券则下跌，因为数据显示经济韧性以及中东冲突仍然受到控制的猜测增多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 22:08:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布伦特原油价格因伊朗袭击以色列而平静下来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油摆脱了伊朗对以色列前所未有的袭击的影响，因猜测冲突将继续得到遏制，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 22:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
